The,Mozilla,Settings,API,supports,the,selection,and,management,of,preferred,settings,in,mobile,devices,and,smartphones,It,allows,developers,to,provide,access,and,change,options,as,well,as,settings,parameters,for,monitoring,devices,The,API,is,only,accessible,to,certified,applications,due,to,the,sensitive,nature,of,system,information